						               													<description>Villain is an immersive group/party game that gives each player roles and tasks to perform while trying to out the player who has the role of the &amp;ldquo;villain.&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The best part is that you can play it for 5 minutes or 5 hours and it will be just as fun! Ages 8+ recommended, but younger have fun too, and can be teamed up with older players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this fast and exciting party game, you will pretend that your house or other building you are in is a town. Each player will have a Character card that will tell you Who you are. You also get a Job card to Do. There are many Job cards in these decks, so you can continue having fun playing over and over!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;However, if you are a citizen doing your job, you will want to watch your back because someone is a VILLAIN. The Villain is KNOCKING OUT (tapping), as many people as they can. If the Villain avoids getting caught and Knocks Out key citizens they win! But, if the Villain is caught and accused or enough tasks are completed CITIZENS win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
